  "texts": [
    "Feature Engineering: The prediction model used in this application includes two prime features: Skill Match Score: This feature calculates the extent of relevant skills overlap.",
    "Semantic Similarity Score: This score captures contextual similarity between the resume and job description.",
    "Prediction and Categorization:After uploading the trained model, the system accepts the skill match and similarity scores that result from it and gives a prediction of the applicant's likelihood.",
    "The output label \"Good Fit\" or \"Not a Good Fit\" enables the hiring managers to make quick evaluation decisions about compatibility.",
    "Application Flow and User InterfaceThe user interface lets the users interact with the application very intuitively and provides for a natural flow:1."
